issue.body:
A stolen SolGov vault craft crewed by ruthless pirates looking to plunder any space stations in the nearby sectors. Inspired by the beestation pirate shuttle this pirate shuttle is intended for use in admemes or whenever someone wants to code pirate midrounds. Pirates will need to spawn with magboots as this does not have grav. Only spawner I've placed on it for now is a captain spawner so that it's spawnable. argh
